1
00:00:42,917 --> 00:00:46,087
[electricity pulsating]

2
00:00:51,092 --> 00:00:52,510
How are we gonna get out of here?

3
00:00:52,844 --> 00:00:53,928
I have an idea.

4
00:00:54,596 --> 00:00:55,597
Which is?

5
00:00:56,306 --> 00:00:59,517
Just set those things to stun.
We're not trying to kill anyone.

6
00:00:59,934 --> 00:01:01,311
Yeah, well, tell that to them.

7
00:01:01,394 --> 00:01:02,562
[pulsating continues]

8
00:01:03,438 --> 00:01:04,689
They're almost through.

9
00:01:05,231 --> 00:01:06,066
Wait.

10
00:01:07,984 --> 00:01:08,818
Wait.

11
00:01:10,362 --> 00:01:11,196
Now!

12
00:01:11,279 --> 00:01:12,739
-[screams]
-[groans]

13
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:14,491
-[groans]
-[groans]

14
00:01:25,502 --> 00:01:26,753
[screams]

15
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,714
R7, find us a path out of here.

16
00:01:29,798 --> 00:01:31,132
[R7 beeps]

17
00:01:36,930 --> 00:01:37,931
[groans]

18
00:01:38,890 --> 00:01:40,141
[R7 beeps]

19
00:01:45,146 --> 00:01:47,232
All right. Now what?

20
00:01:47,482 --> 00:01:48,983
[R7 beeps]

21
00:01:49,067 --> 00:01:52,487
The escape pods have been destroyed.
Taking a shuttle is our best bet.

22
00:01:53,321 --> 00:01:54,322
[Cheep beeps]

23
00:01:54,406 --> 00:01:57,325
[clone trooper groans, exhales deeply]

24
00:01:57,826 --> 00:01:59,577
[Rex] The boys are having
a rough time of it.

25
00:02:00,286 --> 00:02:01,788
Did you hear Maul also escaped?

26
00:02:02,247 --> 00:02:04,249
He didn't escape. I let him out.

27
00:02:04,708 --> 00:02:06,376
What? Why?

28
00:02:06,459 --> 00:02:08,044
Diversion. Come on!

29
00:02:08,878 --> 00:02:10,380
That's one word for it.

30
00:02:10,672 --> 00:02:11,506
[radio beeps]

31
00:02:11,589 --> 00:02:13,675
[clone trooper on radio] Target number
one's escaped the medical bay.

32
00:02:13,758 --> 00:02:14,759
We're in pursuit.

33
00:02:15,176 --> 00:02:17,804
[Jesse on radio]
What is the status of CT-7567?

34
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:20,223
[clone trooper] Commander Rex
is still missing in action, sir.

35
00:02:20,724 --> 00:02:22,225
[Jesse] Did he aid in Tano's escape?

36
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,685
[clone trooper] Unknown at present.

37
00:02:23,768 --> 00:02:24,769
[radio beeps]

38
00:02:28,606 --> 00:02:29,607
[groans]

39
00:02:36,573 --> 00:02:37,574
-[grunts]
-[screams]

40
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:39,868
[screams]

41
00:02:41,619 --> 00:02:43,329
Target number two
is in the hyperdrive room!

42
00:02:45,874 --> 00:02:47,709
-[groans]
-[screams]

43
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:51,755
[grunts]

44
00:02:53,798 --> 00:02:54,632
[screams]

45
00:03:05,602 --> 00:03:07,645
[electricity crackling]

46
00:03:15,236 --> 00:03:16,071
[alarm blaring]

47
00:03:16,154 --> 00:03:18,239
Sir, the hyperdrive generators
are failing!

48
00:03:19,449 --> 00:03:20,825
Disengage! Disengage!

49
00:03:20,909 --> 00:03:21,951
It's too late!

50
00:03:30,418 --> 00:03:31,670
[screaming]

51
00:03:59,197 --> 00:04:00,865
[alarm blaring]

52
00:04:00,949 --> 00:04:02,534
Oh, I don't like the sound of that.

53
00:04:06,746 --> 00:04:07,580
[grunts]

54
00:04:08,832 --> 00:04:12,460
[Rex] Hangar bay doors are sealed.
They've got everything locked down.

55
00:04:13,044 --> 00:04:15,213
If they weren't trying to kill us,
I'd be proud.

56
00:04:16,256 --> 00:04:18,425
R7, start unlocking the doors on bay 12.

57
00:04:18,508 --> 00:04:19,342
[beeps]

58
00:04:19,426 --> 00:04:21,553
-Cheep, prep the shuttle.
-[beeps]

59
00:04:21,636 --> 00:04:23,513
G-G, find out what happened to the ship.

60
00:04:23,596 --> 00:04:24,556
[beeps]

61
00:04:26,141 --> 00:04:27,267
[alarm blaring continues]

62
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:28,351
-Watch it!
-Look out!

63
00:04:31,062 --> 00:04:32,063
[droids beep]

64
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,401
[radio beeps]

65
00:04:36,484 --> 00:04:37,986
[clone trooper on radio]
Control failed to report in.

66
00:04:38,403 --> 00:04:40,947
We think they'll make their move
to escape via the main hangar.

67
00:04:41,239 --> 00:04:44,826
[Jesse on radio] Affirmative, I want
squads marshaled at position 2-5 and 2-7.

68
00:04:44,909 --> 00:04:46,828
Wait for my signal before proceeding.

69
00:04:46,911 --> 00:04:47,954
[clone trooper] Copy that, Lieutenant.

70
00:04:48,038 --> 00:04:48,872
[radio beeps]

71
00:04:49,914 --> 00:04:51,207
[G-G beeps]

72
00:04:51,291 --> 00:04:53,501
What do you mean
the hyperdrive is off-line?

73
00:04:53,585 --> 00:04:55,086
[beeps]

74
00:04:55,170 --> 00:04:57,756
Destroyed? It's completely gone?

75
00:04:58,340 --> 00:05:00,300
-[beeps]
-[computer beeping]

76
00:05:01,676 --> 00:05:04,637
[Rex] We're caught
in that moon's gravitational field.

77
00:05:04,721 --> 00:05:06,639
[beeping continues]

78
00:05:09,017 --> 00:05:11,686
R7, open the main hangar doors.

79
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:14,397
[beeping]

80
00:05:34,084 --> 00:05:35,502
We need to get out of here.

81
00:05:44,135 --> 00:05:47,138
-[alarm blaring continues]
-[explosions]

82
00:05:58,942 --> 00:06:00,026
[Rex] Any luck with those doors?

83
00:06:00,110 --> 00:06:01,111
[R7 beeps]

84
00:06:01,986 --> 00:06:02,987
And the shuttle?

85
00:06:03,071 --> 00:06:04,531
[beeping]

86
00:06:05,323 --> 00:06:06,324
[alert blares]

87
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:11,871
There it is.

88
00:06:15,834 --> 00:06:17,919
-Go!
-I can see them there!

89
00:06:18,003 --> 00:06:18,920
Go, go, go!

90
00:06:20,296 --> 00:06:21,798
[Rex] They were waiting for us.

91
00:06:33,143 --> 00:06:34,686
[Jesse] Hold your position, men.

92
00:06:34,769 --> 00:06:37,772
If they try to leave,
they'll have to go through us.

93
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:41,776
[Rex] So what do we do?
Fight our way to the shuttle?

94
00:06:43,028 --> 00:06:44,446
They're too many.

95
00:06:44,529 --> 00:06:47,449
Besides, I don't wanna hurt them.

96
00:06:49,117 --> 00:06:52,203
[Rex] I hate to tell you this,
but they don't care.

97
00:06:53,455 --> 00:06:57,125
This ship is going down,
and those soldiers, my brothers,

98
00:06:57,208 --> 00:07:01,296
are willing to die and take you and me
along with them.

99
00:07:21,941 --> 00:07:24,402
You're a good soldier, Rex.

100
00:07:24,486 --> 00:07:26,946
So is every one of those men down there.

101
00:07:27,572 --> 00:07:32,911
They may be willing to die, but I am not
the one who is going to kill them.

102
00:07:40,126 --> 00:07:42,045
So, we're just gonna surrender?

103
00:07:43,338 --> 00:07:46,549
Admit defeat? Is that it?

104
00:07:48,551 --> 00:07:49,552
No.

105
00:07:50,845 --> 00:07:53,014
Well, I don't see any other option.

106
00:08:07,696 --> 00:08:09,239
I have an idea.

107
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:13,493
Don't worry. It's a good one... I think.

108
00:08:15,745 --> 00:08:17,330
Can I count on the three of you?

109
00:08:17,414 --> 00:08:19,290
[R7 beeps]

110
00:08:19,374 --> 00:08:21,751
[Cheep beeps]

111
00:08:21,835 --> 00:08:23,420
Good. I'll explain on the way.

112
00:08:23,503 --> 00:08:24,754
[G-G beeps]

113
00:08:30,427 --> 00:08:31,428
[radio beeps]

114
00:08:31,511 --> 00:08:34,180
[clone trooper on radio] Sir, we think
Maul might be headed your way. Be aware.

115
00:08:34,264 --> 00:08:35,557
[Rex] Hold your fire!

116
00:08:41,021 --> 00:08:42,814
[Jesse] Hang on.
We have Tano and the commander.

117
00:08:42,897 --> 00:08:44,733
Send all remaining troops to my position.

118
00:08:47,152 --> 00:08:50,822
[Rex] I said hold your fire, Jesse.
I have the situation under control.

119
00:08:51,656 --> 00:08:55,994
[Jesse] You have your order, sir.
Now execute it or I will!

120
00:08:57,620 --> 00:09:01,666
[Rex] The order was to execute the Jedi
for treason against the Republic.

121
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:06,463
The problem is,
Ahsoka Tano is no longer a Jedi.

122
00:09:06,546 --> 00:09:07,881
Hasn't been for some time.

123
00:09:09,591 --> 00:09:10,592
[droid beeps]

124
00:09:13,970 --> 00:09:19,434
[Jesse] Sir, you said yourself we're under
special order from Darth Sidious

125
00:09:19,517 --> 00:09:25,106
to eliminate Ahsoka Tano
and any other clone who disobeys Order 66.

126
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:26,024
[R7 beeps]

127
00:09:26,941 --> 00:09:29,527
Just keep him talking,
a little bit longer.

128
00:09:31,446 --> 00:09:33,698
[Rex] Jesse. Jesse, listen to me.

129
00:09:33,782 --> 00:09:35,450
We've known each other a long time.

130
00:09:35,533 --> 00:09:40,455
If we don't get this right, we will be
the ones committing treason, not her.

131
00:09:44,042 --> 00:09:48,046
[Jesse] Commander Rex,
you're in violation of Order 66.

132
00:09:48,129 --> 00:09:51,383
I accuse you of treason
against the Grand Army of the Republic.

133
00:09:51,466 --> 00:09:55,387
You'll be demoted in rank from commander
and subject to execution

134
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:57,555
along with the traitor Ahsoka Tano.

135
00:09:58,264 --> 00:09:59,224
[R7 beeps]

136
00:09:59,307 --> 00:10:00,141
[Cheep beeps]

137
00:10:00,725 --> 00:10:01,726
Ready?

138
00:10:03,061 --> 00:10:05,563
[Rex] Yeah, I didn't much like
being a commander anyway.

139
00:10:05,647 --> 00:10:09,109
-[Jesse] Company, ready. Aim!
-[alert blares]

140
00:10:09,192 --> 00:10:10,110
Now!

141
00:10:10,735 --> 00:10:12,570
[clone troopers screaming]

142
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:14,823
[grunts, screams]

143
00:10:18,076 --> 00:10:18,910
[groans]

144
00:10:34,134 --> 00:10:35,802
[G-G beeping]

145
00:10:35,885 --> 00:10:36,970
Rex, the ship.

146
00:10:45,311 --> 00:10:47,522
You wanted this chaos.

147
00:10:47,605 --> 00:10:48,440
[grunts]

148
00:10:51,109 --> 00:10:52,527
[Maul screams]

149
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:53,445
[grunts]

150
00:11:15,842 --> 00:11:16,760
[grunts]

151
00:11:16,843 --> 00:11:17,927
[Jesse] Move it. Move it.

152
00:11:18,011 --> 00:11:20,305
Get these lifts activated.
Get us up there.

153
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,890
[clone technician] Our panel's locked out.

154
00:11:21,973 --> 00:11:23,183
[R7 beeps]

155
00:11:23,266 --> 00:11:24,601
[Jesse] Fire on those droids.

156
00:11:25,477 --> 00:11:27,145
[R7 beeps]

157
00:11:43,328 --> 00:11:44,329
The shuttle.

158
00:11:47,582 --> 00:11:48,583
[Maul gasps]

159
00:11:50,210 --> 00:11:51,169
[grunts]

160
00:11:55,548 --> 00:11:56,383
[grunts]

161
00:11:58,385 --> 00:12:00,053
-[Rex grunts]
-[R7 beeps]

162
00:12:00,136 --> 00:12:01,471
[beeping]

163
00:12:02,847 --> 00:12:03,932
[Rex] Incoming.

164
00:12:04,015 --> 00:12:05,642
-[clone trooper] Surround them!
-[Ahsoka grunts]

165
00:12:06,434 --> 00:12:07,435
[grunts]

166
00:12:11,981 --> 00:12:12,816
[R7 beeps]

167
00:12:13,483 --> 00:12:14,609
[R7 screams]

168
00:12:23,368 --> 00:12:24,202
[grunts]

169
00:12:24,285 --> 00:12:26,413
[Rex] Can't hold them off.
Too many of them.

170
00:12:26,996 --> 00:12:27,956
[growls]

171
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,064
[screams]

172
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:06,745
[screams]

173
00:13:17,088 --> 00:13:20,008
[Rex grunts, breathes heavily]

174
00:13:26,848 --> 00:13:27,766
[sighs]

175
00:13:28,266 --> 00:13:29,267
[Jesse] Blast them.

176
00:13:31,770 --> 00:13:33,146
[Cheep beeps]

177
00:13:33,229 --> 00:13:34,481
[screaming]

178
00:13:34,939 --> 00:13:36,358
[clone troopers shouting, grunting]

179
00:13:36,691 --> 00:13:37,525
[Cheep beeps]

180
00:13:37,609 --> 00:13:38,526
[Jesse] Hey.

181
00:13:38,610 --> 00:13:40,987
[Cheep whistles, beeps]

182
00:13:42,697 --> 00:13:44,032
[Jesse] Blast those dirty droids.

183
00:13:44,491 --> 00:13:46,117
[droids scream]

184
00:13:54,084 --> 00:13:54,918
[grunts]

185
00:13:57,128 --> 00:13:58,129
[screams]

186
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:02,717
[Rex] Nothing. Nothing. Nothing.

187
00:14:03,218 --> 00:14:04,886
Everything down here is under maintenance.

188
00:14:08,682 --> 00:14:09,683
There!

189
00:14:16,314 --> 00:14:17,399
[Rex] Get me over there.

190
00:14:28,535 --> 00:14:29,786
[Rex screams]

191
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:32,747
[grunts]

192
00:14:36,710 --> 00:14:37,961
[groans]

193
00:14:40,714 --> 00:14:41,548
[grunts]

194
00:14:44,592 --> 00:14:45,427
[grunts]

195
00:14:50,306 --> 00:14:52,809
We've entered the atmosphere.
Fire retro-rockets.

196
00:14:52,892 --> 00:14:55,228
We've lost lateral control.
We're gonna break apart--

197
00:14:59,983 --> 00:15:01,443
-Look out!
-[screaming]

198
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,321
[screaming]

199
00:15:09,034 --> 00:15:10,827
[screaming]

200
00:15:13,079 --> 00:15:14,080
[Rex] Come on.

201
00:15:27,344 --> 00:15:29,137
-[groans]
-[controls beep]

202
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:46,654
[controls beep]

203
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:43,211
[explosions]

204
00:19:38,094 --> 00:19:41,097
[droid beeping]

205
00:19:53,026 --> 00:19:56,780
[Darth Vader breathing]

206
00:20:09,751 --> 00:20:12,754
[breathing continues]

207
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:32,857
[lightsaber buzzes, hums]

208
00:20:32,941 --> 00:20:36,444
-[breathing continues]
-[bird squawks]

209
00:20:51,334 --> 00:20:52,419
[lightsaber buzzes]

210
00:20:56,214 --> 00:20:58,216
[breathing continues]

